					<b class="mediaTitle">
						Archive: Bloody Sunday<br />
						<span>An overview of the events of 30 January 1972 in Londonderry, Northern Ireland, using archive footage and interviews.</span>
					</b>
				</a>
					
			<img width="640" height="360" alt="Demonstrators on a civil rights march through the streets of Londonderry before the shootings on Bloody Sunday" src="/web/20140914231102im_/http://static.bbc.co.uk/history/img/ic/640/images/resources/histories/bloody_sunday.jpg"/>
		
